thread.title: BRIEF-Cybaero Evaluates Existing Liquidity, Say Cannot Rule Out Bankruptcy​

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Cybaero Evaluates Existing Liquidity, Say Cannot Rule Out Bankruptcy​
text:
Feb 16 (Reuters) - Cybaero Ab:
* COMMENTS REGARDING FINANCIAL SITUATION IN CYBAERO AB * ‍IS CURRENTLY EXAMINING HOW LONG EXISTING LIQUIDITY IS SUFFICIENT TO RUN COMPANY​
* ‍IS CURRENTLY DISCUSSING WITH OTHER FINANCIERS ABOUT OPPORTUNITY TO SOLVE EMERGING SITUATIO​
* ‍IF DISCUSSIONS ARE NOT SUCCESSFUL A BANKRUPTCY COULD NOT BE RULED OUT.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
